WEBVTT

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.616
Ustozning hafsalasi pir bo’lib,

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:04.296
“Kimdir bu insonlar haqida ham 
biror iliq so’z aytadimi?”

00:01:04.319 --> 00:01:05.536
(Kulgu)

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:08.536
“Hech kim? Mayli, sovg’angizni
olingda, joyingizga o'tiring.

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:09.816
O’zingizni yaxshi tuting,

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:11.936
kelasi yil kimdir siz haqda
iliq so’z aytar.

00:01:11.960 --> 00:01:13.720
(Kulgu)

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:16.136
Tasvirlab berishimdan

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:18.536
buni juda yaxshi esga olishimni
bilgandirsiz.

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:20.160
(Kulgu)

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:22.896
Biroq o’sha kuni kim o’zini yomonroq his

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:25.096
qilganini bilmayman.
Menmi yoki o’qituvchi?

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:28.256
U jamoani shakllantirish jarayonini
3 nafar 6 yasharlik bolalar

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:31.080
uchun hajviy ko’rsatuvga
aylantirganini tushungandir.